      <p><strong>&ldquo;AI is hype.&rdquo;</strong> Some of it is. Receipts are how you tell the difference &mdash; everything I claim here links to something you can open and check.</p>
      <p><strong>&ldquo;This is just freelancing with a manifesto.&rdquo;</strong> Freelancing sells hours. What I build compounds; each project becomes a kit that runs without me.</p>
    </section>

    <hr />

    <section id="masterplan">
