        <li><strong>Use that to compound.</strong> Kits become systems that run without me. Cheaper to own, no lock-in.</li>
        <li><strong>Then the leverage belongs to everyone.</strong> What used to take a funded company becomes something any operator runs alone.</li>
      </ol>
